---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Location & Arrival Guide | Ellamin Courtyard Retreat" description="Location, nearby landmarks, arrival confidence, and route planning for Ellamin Courtyard Retreat in Morib, Banting.">
  <section class="v3-band pb-12">
    <div class="v3-container">
      <div class="v3-split">
        <div>
          <p class="v3-eyebrow">Location guide</p>
          <h1 class="v3-section-title mt-3 font-display">Arrival should feel known before the drive.</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[1.02rem] leading-8 text-[color:var(--muted)]">
          Ellamin Courtyard is positioned as a private pool retreat near Morib, Banting. This page is a decision mockup: the exact map pin and travel times should be confirmed by the host, but the guest-facing structure is complete.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-stretch">
        <figure class="v3-media-frame min-h-[420px] lg:col-span-7">
          <img class="v3-theme-day" src="/images/ellamin-courtyard-day-panorama.png" alt="Daytime wide view of Ellamin Courtyard pool, house, gazebo, BBQ bay, and lawn" loading="eager" />
          <img class="v3-theme-night" src="/images/ellamin-courtyard-night-panorama.png" alt="Night panorama of Ellamin Courtyard with illuminated pool, house, gazebo, and BBQ bay" loading="eager" />
          <figcaption class="v3-media-label">Use this view for orientation: pool left, house center, BBQ and dining bay right</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5 grid gap-4">
          <article class="v3-card p-6">
            <p class="v3-eyebrow">Arrival confidence</p>
            <h2 class="font-display mt-2 text-[clamp(31px,4vw,48px)] font-black leading-none">What guests need before WhatsApp</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted)]">
              The location page should reduce uncertainty: where the retreat sits, what landmarks are nearby, where vehicles go, and what message the guest sends when asking for the pin.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="v3-card p-6">
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold">Host-confirmed pin</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-[color:var(--muted)]">
              Exact Google Maps pin should be sent after the booking request includes dates, pax, number of vehicles, and stay purpose.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Morib+Banting" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="v3-button v3-button-primary mt-5">Open Morib, Banting Map</a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="v3-container">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <p class="v3-eyebrow">Nearby proof</p>
          <h2 class="v3-section-title mt-3 font-display">Landmarks by guest need.</h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted)]">
            These are placeholder planning distances for the mockup. Replace with host-verified values before public launch.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-7 grid gap-3">
          {[
            ['Kelanang / Morib beach drive', 'Useful for families planning a beach-and-pool weekend.'],
            ['Seafood and local dinner stops', 'Useful for guests who want low-prep meals after pool time.'],
            ['Convenience shops and breakfast stalls', 'Useful for ice, charcoal, snacks, and morning food runs.'],
            ['KLIA / Klang Valley access', 'Useful for outstation family or corporate retreat planning.']
          ].map(([title, copy]) => (
            <article class="v3-card p-5">
              <strong class="block text-lg">{title}</strong>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[color:var(--muted)]">{copy}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-24">
    <div class="v3-container">
      <div class="v3-card p-6 md:p-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5">
            <p class="v3-eyebrow">Mock map structure</p>
            <h2 class="font-display mt-2 text-[clamp(31px,4vw,48px)] font-black leading-none">Pin, route, arrival, parking.</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-7 text-[color:var(--muted)]">
              This is intentionally schematic. It shows what the page should communicate before replacing it with a verified embedded map or static map image.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="lg:col-span-7">
            <div class="relative min-h-[320px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-[color:var(--line)] bg-[color:var(--warm)] p-5">
              <div class="absolute left-[8%] top-[18%] h-24 w-40 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--pool)]/30 bg-[color:var(--pool)]/10"></div>
              <div class="absolute right-[10%] top-[12%] h-52 w-36 rotate-12 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--line)] bg-[color:var(--paper)]"></div>
              <div class="absolute left-[32%] top-[52%] h-3 w-[48%] -rotate-6 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--gold)]"></div>
              <div class="absolute left-[18%] top-[36%] h-3 w-[58%] rotate-12 rounded-full bg-[color:var(--canopy-soft)]/45"></div>
              <div class="absolute left-[54%] top-[45%] rounded-full bg-[color:var(--deep-pool)] px-4 py-2 text-sm font-[850] text-white">Ellamin Courtyard</div>
              <div class="absolute left-[10%] top-[70%] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--muted)]">Coastal route</div>
              <div class="absolute right-[12%] bottom-[16%] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--muted)]">Town / shops</div>
              <div class="absolute left-[12%] top-[23%] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.12em] text-[color:var(--pool)]">Beach side</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
